de9f53aa-fa15-45cf-ba9a-d371c91c31da.title: Bob Barter (herbs)
de9f53aa-fa15-45cf-ba9a-d371c91c31da.text:
Hello, chum, fancy buyin' some designer jewellery?
They've come all the way from Ardougne! Most pukka!

26d52426-0435-4d45-b443-448003e7b66f.title: <player>
26d52426-0435-4d45-b443-448003e7b66f.text: Erm, no. I'm all set, thanks.

ba62f308-a885-4987-9de1-3d277e9d40e5.title: Bob Barter (herbs)
ba62f308-a885-4987-9de1-3d277e9d40e5.text:
Okay, chum, so what can I do for you? I can tell you
the very latest herb & potion prices, or perhaps I could
help you decant your potions.

options.text: Can you show me the prices for herbs and potions?
Can you decant things for me?

43c9a6d5-db49-4ad4-8d07-301fa80fd433.title: Bob Barter (herbs)
43c9a6d5-db49-4ad4-8d07-301fa80fd433.text: Why, I'm Bob! Your friendly seller of smashin' goods!

3ef809d4-e991-4cd4-9f4a-67102bafafed.title: <player>
3ef809d4-e991-4cd4-9f4a-67102bafafed.text: So what do you have to sell?

89363d54-736d-4b7c-822a-16d18ca15d6d.title: Bob Barter (herbs)
89363d54-736d-4b7c-822a-16d18ca15d6d.text:
Oh, not much at the moment. Cuz, ya know, business
being so well and cushie.

68ced74a-05f7-4e1d-a12c-ce02d9bda58c.title: <player>
68ced74a-05f7-4e1d-a12c-ce02d9bda58c.text: You don't really look like you're being so successful.

e8900212-080f-4013-9b1a-46e010ee457d.title: Bob Barter (herbs)
e8900212-080f-4013-9b1a-46e010ee457d.text:
You plonka! It's all a show, innit! If I let people knows
I'm in good business they'll want a share of the moolah!

eb19dad9-062b-46c4-85ca-0089eed8dad6.title: <player>
eb19dad9-062b-46c4-85ca-0089eed8dad6.text: You conveniently have a response for everything.

06111600-4392-467e-8c4c-e15a28cd3877.title: Bob Barter (herbs)
06111600-4392-467e-8c4c-e15a28cd3877.text: That's the Ardougne way, my friend.

options.text: Can you show me the prices for herbs and potions?
Can you decant things for me?

84f9c5f7-72d3-4236-9a25-e549540dd8b0.title: <player>
84f9c5f7-72d3-4236-9a25-e549540dd8b0.text: Can you decant things for me?
